title: 30 vehicles ram into each other on Jaipur- Agra Highway due to fog; 1 dead, 28 dead - SEE PICS
text:
News » India ﻿ 30 vehicles ram into each other on Jaipur- Agra Highway due to fog; 1 dead, 28 dead - SEE PICS Last Updated: Sunday, January 29, 2017 - 12:02 0 
Jaipur: In an unfortunate incident, almost 30 vehicles rammed into each other on Jaipur-Agra Highway due to fog. 
Reportedly, 1 person died so far. 
Also, 28 were injured out of which 3 are critical.   12:02 More from zeenews
